<p>Raphael Pierzina wrote a cool article about how to run use a hook function to only run tests that use a particular fixture. However, I wanted to make it more generic so I could pass in the fixture via command line option. Minor tweak to add options. Thanks Raphael @hackebrot for doing most of the [&#8230;]</p>
